}}'''Malaysia''' is a [[Nations|country]] that was on BitLife in October 2019. Its default cities are the capital, Kuala Lumpur, along with George Town.

Malaysia was added as a new country to BitLife in late October 2019 during the Haunted Update, as the only non-Haunted addition to the game. [[Czech Republic]], [[Ecuador]], [[Hong Kong]], [[Monaco]], [[Morocco]], [[Pakistan]], and [[Syria]] were also added at the same time.
